parameters: \n<\N[5]>\F[62]So, it was you after all... Kino.

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]I wanted to talk to you without Sawa around. Huh?
Don't give me that scary look and be on guard.

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F]Before we start talking, could you please lock the door
to that hallway? Just in case.

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]If that caution had been displayed from the
beginning, we might not have ended up in this
situation, huh?
\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F](Indeed... I have no words to retort on that point)

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Well, fine. But... I'll make sure you can't escape
while I'm not here, okay?
!$マネージャー(座)

\n<\N[5]>\F[61](Even if you go through the trouble of moving to the
bed, there's no way you can escape...)

\F[61]When I moved to the bed... I remembered the time when
Kino helped me and accidentally touched her skin.
\n<\N[5]>\F[61](It was soft... and it had a nice scent too...)

\F[61]My crotch is throbbing... but I suppose that can't
be helped. Kino, who claims to be in charge of
visuals, has a baby face but a well-proportioned
and beautiful face when seen from the side. She's
quite the beauty.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61](Originally, she was just a underground idol... but I
discovered a strange charisma in her that was
different from Neon, so I scouted her.)

\n<\N[5]>\F[61](We had a big argument back then... You were adamant
about not betraying our comrades.)

\F[61]In the end, Kino was persuaded by our comrades and
ended up joining the members. And even now, I know
that she still keeps in touch with our old
comrades.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61](Of course he would be angry... He's someone who
cares about his comrades more than anyone else.)
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...Well then, shall we begin?

\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]The sound of the lock being closed behind me echoes
in the room. A shiver runs down my spine... That's
right, this is it.

In contrast to the overwhelming performance and
beauty that attracts everyone, Minato possesses a
captivating charisma, but hers...

A unique sense of fear that is not befitting of her
baby face. It makes others instinctively bow down
and feel relieved. Her charisma of domination. She
possessed that... It's only now, in a time like
this, that I finally understand.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]I don't have any intention of prying into your and
Sawa's affairs. That's a matter between the two of
you, and it's not an issue for an outsider like me
to interfere in.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]However, that is... a story for after settling the score.
I will make sure to fully compensate for the sin
of making Sawa cry right here.
\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Sin? From the mouth of a traitor...
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Ah, that's why... This is also my atonement.
\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Kino slowly approaches while saying that.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F](What the hell... What does this person intend to do to
me? D-Don't tell me they're going to kill me...
Ugh! Run----...)

Due to fear, my body trembles and stiffens. In
addition, numbness spreads to my limbs, and I am
completely embodying the situation of a frog being
stared at by a snake.

\n<\N[5]>(I-I have no choice but to persuade... Damn it... If
necessary, even beg for my life...)

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Wait a minute! It's a bit exaggerated, isn't it? Just
because I used Sawa's mouth a little...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Did you use her...? Perhaps Sawa wasn't crying
because she was used, but because you ended up
like that...

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F](Tch... Is this backfiring?! Damn it, I won't die in a
place like this!!)
\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]W-Wait... Please don't kill me...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]You're so disgusting... I didn't want to see you like
this...

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF](T-This is no good... They're completely brainwashed...
No matter what I say...)
